Package: dissmapr
Title: Workflow for Compositional Dissimilarity and Biodiversity Turnover Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sandra", "MacFadyen",
           email = "macfadyen@sun.ac.za",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5316-440X")),
    person("Stellenbosch University", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Tools to compute and map biodiversity turnover at the
    macroscale. Provides functions for generating spatial grids, retrieving
    environmental data, computing multi-order zeta diversity, fitting
    I-spline models for generalised dissimilarity, predicting community
    turnover, and delineating and mapping bioregions and their changes
    over time.
